structure.unit: A JUSTICE AND PUBLIC SAFETY CABINET

law.catch_line: Justice and Public Safety Cabinet may provide state resources to Trooper Island.
law.text: The Justice and Public Safety Cabinet and its agencies may provide state personnel, state property, and other state resources to Trooper Island Incorporated.
law.history: Amended 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 85, sec. 49, effective June 26, 2007. -- Created 2002 Ky. Acts ch. 290, sec. 3, effective April 9, 2002.
